<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr" class="h-full bg-gray-50">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sayfa Bulunamadı - 404</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="h-full flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-md w-full text-center p-8">
        <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-8">
            <div class="mx-auto h-16 w-16 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle text-red-600 text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
            
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                404
            </h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">
                Sayfa Bulunamadı
            </h3>
            
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Aradığınız sayfa mevcut değil, taşınmış veya silinmiş olabilir.
            </p>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
                    <a 
                        href="/" 
                        class="flex-1 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-medium py-3 px-4 rounded-md transition-colors text-center"
                    >
                        <i class="fas fa-home mr-2"></i>Ana Sayfa
                    </a>
                    <button 
                        onclick="history.back()" 
                        class="flex-1 bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 font-medium py-3 px-4 rounded-md transition-colors text-center"
                    >
                        <i class="fas fa-arrow-left mr-2"></i>Geri Dön
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>